<!--pages/home/home.wxml-->
<view class="l-class card-container card-container-avatar card-container-avatar-left card-container-unfull"
    wx:for="{{2}}" wx:key="index">
    <view class="card-avatar-top">
        <view class="card-avatar-left" bindtap="toUser">
            <image mode="aspectFill" class="l-img-class card-img-avatar"
                src="http://cdn.wowyou.cc/179982212_3572937446140541_336041814125647551_n.jpeg" lazy-load>
            </image>
            <view class="card-avatar">
                <text class="l-title-class card-title card-title-avatar">七月</text>
                <text class="describe">10小时前</text>
            </view>
        </view>
        <van-tag round color="#f3f3f3" text-color="#3963BC" size="large" plain>
            + 关注
        </van-tag>
    </view>
    <view class="avter-content">
        很简单，豆瓣现在这样就给大家指了一条明路:以后凡是这种国产的风口浪尖的的片子，会涉及到各方背后利益关系的片子...
    </view>
    <view class="avter-share-img">
        <swiper indicator-dots="true" style="height:120vw;">
            <swiper-item>
                <view class="swiper-item">
                    <image mode="widthFix" style="width:100vw;"
                        src="http://cdn.wowyou.cc/179982212_3572937446140541_336041814125647551_n.jpeg">
                    </image>
                </view>
            </swiper-item>
            <swiper-item>
                <view class="swiper-item">
                    <image mode="widthFix" style="width:100vw;"
                        src="http://cdn.wowyou.cc/179982212_3572937446140541_336041814125647551_n.jpeg">
                    </image>
                </view>
            </swiper-item>
        </swiper>
    </view>
    <view class="avter-share-container">
        <view class="like-container">
            <van-icon name="like-o" color="#666" size="23" />
            <view class="number">160000次赞</view>
        </view>
        <view class="share-container">
            <van-icon name="share-o" color="#666" size="23" />
        </view>
        <view class="download-container" bindtap="download" data-src="http://cdn.wowyou.cc/179982212_3572937446140541_336041814125647551_n.jpeg,http://cdn.wowyou.cc/179966113_162709649104940_7087972947059416111_n.jpeg">
            <van-icon name="down" color="#666" size="23" />
        </view>
    </view>
</view>

<l-tab-bar list="{{list}}" bg-img="https://img.juzibiji.top/20201206200539.png" />